NepaliDatePicker:
    onDateSelect: sets the current date (passed to NepaliCalendar)

    UI Components:
    - NepaliCalendar
    - NepaliDateInput (date object is passed)

NepaliDateInput:
    onBlur: reformats the date
    onChange: updates the value state, shows the error
    onKeyDown: handle enter input

    UI Components:
    - input (dont wrap it other elements, extract className and add it again)